metadata.name: Ether Spirit Diamond
metadata.description:
The Ether Diamond is a talisman of depth of knowledge, instinct and the great mystery of creation. Spinning from within in the void of possibility, the atomic force spectrum is overflowing with magic. This Diamond is from the jewel on the crown of the Divine Mother Kali offering transmutation of all that needs to pass away so that a new world parasympathetic can be born anew.
The Ether Diamond offers its holders a transmission of intuitive seeing, unwavering awareness and self realization. The Solfeggio 741HZ that is embedded in the accompanying soundscape awakens intuition.

Affirmation Mantra: I am an empty vessel for the wisdom of the Divine. There is infinite possibility in the vast universe of cosmic love. I am connected to the source.

attributes.value: For getting solutions and expressing themselves
